'''Lonnie Smith''' (Julayi 3, 1942 - Seputembara 28, 2021), wotchedwa '''Dr. Lonnie Smith''', anali wolemba jazz waku America [[Hammond B3]] yemwe anali membala wa quartet ya [[George Benson]] mzaka za 1960. Adalemba ma albino ndi Louxson wa saxophonist wa Blue Note asanasainidwe ngati solo. Iye anali ndi dzina laulendowu. Smith anabadwira ku Lackawanna, New York, pa Julayi 3, 1942. <ref name="gilbreath">{{cite web|url=http://www.allaboutjazz.com/php/article.php?id=28035|title=Dr. Lonnie Smith: Organ Guru|access-date=January 21, 2008|last=Gilbreath|first=Mikayla|date=January 7, 2008|work=All About Jazz}}</ref> Adaleredwa ndi amayi ake ndi abambo ake omupeza, ndipo banja linali ndi pulogalamu yamawu komanso wayilesi.<ref name="NYT obit">{{cite news|title=Lonnie Smith, Soulful Jazz Organist, Is Dead at 79|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/29/arts/music/lonnie-smith-dead.html|first=Peter|last=Keepnews|date=September 29, 2021|access-date=September 30, 2021|newspaper=The New York Times}}</ref> Ananenanso kuti amayi ake amamukhudza kwambiri pakumuyimba, popeza adamuphunzitsa za nyimbo za gospel, classical, ndi jazz.<ref name="manheim2005">{{Cite book|last=Manheim|first=James M.|title=Contemporary Black Biography|publisher=[[Gale (publisher)|Gale]]|year=2005|isbn=978-1-4144-0548-3|volume=49|location=Detroit|pages=[[iarchive:contemporaryblac0049unse/page/133/mode/1up|133â€“135]]|chapter=Dr. Lonnie Smith|issn=1058-1316|oclc=728680730}}</ref>

